fasper.base
Interface ASTComparator

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultASTComparator
public interface ASTComparator

Comparator common interface. It should be inherited by any AST comparator in order to be plugin-able.

See Also:
DefaultASTComparator, ASTFilter, GMActivation, fasper.gm

useFilter

void useFilter(ASTFilter _filter)
Specify the filter bank to be used. There are situations when you would like to filter out some nodes or ignore whole branches of the tree. Theese are handled by an ASTFilter.

Parameters:
_filter - to be used by this comparator should inherit from ASTFilter
